div.div:
Requirements
- Logs
- Metrics
Logs:
For log collection the server is using a pull base configuration.
Open Telemetry Collector is getting logs from Files and API server and delivering it to VictoriaLogs which stores and provides an UI to query it.
Metrics:
Victoria Metrics collects the logs using ServiceMonitors and aggregates it.
Grafana then, Connects to VictoriaMetrics and populate the desired dashboards.
